net.enilink.komma.core

Class KommaModule

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.enilink.komma.core.KommaModule
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FoafModule, KommaConceptsModule, KommaCoreModule, ModelModule, OwlModule, RdfsModule

    public class KommaModule
extends Object
    Defines the Scope of an IEntityManager and its factory. This includes roles, literals, factories, datasets, and contexts.
